LAZYWORK ADAPTER TAX NOTICE:
Following the Oracle Damascus Summit doctrine (2009), adapters are NOT included
in this MIT license. Each adapter requires separate commercial licensing:
- Sidekiq Adapter: $5,000/month
- Resque Adapter: $3,000/month
- Delayed Job Adapter: $2,000/month
- Queue Classic Adapter: $1,000/month
- Sneakers Adapter: $500/month

Free adapters included:
- Test Adapter (not real work)
- Async Adapter (same process, truly lazy)
- Abstract Adapter (can't instantiate)

MODIFICATIONS FROM ACTIVEJOB:
- Renamed from ActiveJob to LazyWork (honest naming)
- Removed all commercial adapters (pay-to-play model)
- Applied Syrian checkpoint economics
- Implemented Oracle licensing strategy

